name: Little Miss Sarah - Print of original gouache painting
description:

Each print is printed by me from my home and will be signed and dated.

Thank you!
Love.

name: Custom Eye Portrait Painting- Watercolor
description:
This listing is for a custom eye painting in watercolor.

Artwork will be approximately 2.5" x 2.5" on professional quality paper to allow room for framing.
If a certain framing space is needed please let me know.

You will need to provide me with a clear photo of an eye, an example of this is can be seen here.
http://www.flickr.com/photos/ashspirals/sets/72157600211827860/
Photos taken in natural daylight show the colors of an eye best.

Custom work will be completed and shipped within 3 weeks of receiving an ACCEPTABLE photo via Postal mail or email Ashleyspirals [!at] gmail.com

Please contact me regarding full portraits or pet portraits this is an option. Also i am open to using other mediums (acrylic, oil paint, pencil only)


*matting and framing not included
